title: Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick, DP talks to Rick Stroud about Ryan Jensen's injury. How will it affect the Bucs? Mike Florio calls in to discuss Kyler's independent study clause. And Jeff Passan shares the latest on Shohei Ohtani and Juan Soto's trade markets.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
